data.title: 'It'll Definitely Be Remembered': Notorious Ex-Toronto Mayor Rob Ford Dies
data.meta_description: Ford, 46, succumbed to cancer Tuesday, 18 months after doctors discovered a softball-sized malignant tumour in his abdomen
